{"title":"基于容器（docker）的 WRF模式 简易快速部署方案","uid":"03ab3527d41f8e0cc6ed204543909849","slug":"easy-wrf","date":"2020-09-30T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2020-09-30T16:00:00.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/easy-wrf.json","keywords":"Linux, LaTeX, Blog","cover":"https://img.swz128.top/EASY-WRF_File/logo.png","content":"<p><img src=\"https://img.swz128.top/EASY-WRF_File/logo.png\" alt=\"logo\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"Easy-WRF\"><a href=\"#Easy-WRF\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Easy-WRF\"></a>Easy-WRF</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>WRF（Weather Research and Forecasting Model）模式是由NCEP，NCAR等科研机构中心着手开发的一种统一的中尺度天气预报模式。<br>WRF模式系统具有的可移植，易维护，可扩充，高效率，方便等特点，使其成为改进从云尺度到各种不同天气尺度的重要天气特征预报精度的工具。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>但是WRF模式的安装对于初学者来说有一定的困难，因此为了帮助初学者在电脑上快速部署安装WRF模式，就有了该项目，Easy-WRF。</strong></p>\n<p>项目地址：<br>GitHub: <a href=\"https://github.com/SWZ128/easy-wrf\">https://github.com/SWZ128/easy-wrf</a></p>\n<p>本项目是单节点建模运行的容器化WRF，主要用于教学和培训示例，本人不是气象相关专业，谬误在所难免，望海涵。</p>\n<h2 id=\"Features\"><a href=\"#Features\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Features\"></a>Features</h2><ul>\n<li>WPS + WRF（version 3.7.1）</li>\n<li>简易部署（docker）</li>\n<li>优雅易用（Oh-my-zsh）</li>\n<li>精简小巧（镜像1.6GB左右）</li>\n<li>国内部署简易</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Installation-amp-Usage\"><a href=\"#Installation-amp-Usage\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Installation &amp; Usage\"></a>Installation &amp; Usage</h2><h3 id=\"方案1、使用-docker-pull-拉取（推荐）\"><a href=\"#方案1、使用-docker-pull-拉取（推荐）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方案1、使用 docker pull 拉取（推荐）\"></a>方案1、使用 docker pull 拉取（推荐）</h3><p>确保已经安装docker，如果还没有，<a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/docker/centos-docker-install.html\">点击我</a></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker pull swz128&#x2F;easy-wrf</code></pre>\n\n<p>检查镜像是否拉取成功</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker images</code></pre>\n\n<p>得到类似下方的输出</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">REPOSITORY        TAG       IMAGE ID       CREATED             SIZE\nswz128&#x2F;easy-wrf   latest    2c04b5c62a0b   About an hour ago   1.6GB</code></pre>\n\n<p>run</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker run -v 需要挂载的本地目录:容器中的目录 -it --name test_001 swz128&#x2F;easy-wrf</code></pre>\n\n<p>例如这样（请将路径修改为自己的）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker run -v &#x2F;Users&#x2F;mac&#x2F;wrf&#x2F;wrf-data:&#x2F;root&#x2F;wrf-data -it --name test_001 swz128&#x2F;easy-wrf</code></pre>\n\n<p>现在就可以愉快地学习和使用了</p>\n<p>停止容器</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker stop test_001</code></pre>\n\n<p>当退出并停止容器后，可以使用如下命令再次进入</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker start test_001\ndocker exec -it test_001 &#x2F;bin&#x2F;zsh</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"方案2、使用-docker-build\"><a href=\"#方案2、使用-docker-build\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方案2、使用 docker build\"></a>方案2、使用 docker build</h3><p>将项目克隆到本地</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;swz128&#x2F;easy-wrf.git\ncd easy-wrf&#x2F;</code></pre>\n\n<p>Build</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">docker build -t esay-wrf .</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"Support\"><a href=\"#Support\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Support\"></a>Support</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www2.mmm.ucar.edu/wrf/users/docs/user_guide_V3/user_guide_V3.8/contents.html\">官方文档</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wrf-model/WRF/\">官方GitHub</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://bbs.06climate.com/\">气象家园论坛</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Acknowledgment\"><a href=\"#Acknowledgment\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Acknowledgment\"></a>Acknowledgment</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/NCAR/container-wrf\">container-wrf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wrf-model/WRF\">WRF</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/davegill/wrf-coop\">wrf-coop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www2.mmm.ucar.edu/wrf/src/\">wrf-src</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"License\"><a href=\"#License\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"License\"></a>License</h2><p>MIT License</p>\n<h2 id=\"版权声明\"><a href=\"#版权声明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"版权声明\"></a>版权声明</h2><ul>\n<li>作者：麟子</li>\n<li>地址：<a href=\"https://swz128.top/post/easy-wrf\">https://swz128.top/post/easy-wrf</a></li>\n<li>协议：<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/deed.zh\">CC BY-SA 4.0</a> 欢迎转载，务必注明出处</li>\n</ul>\n","text":" Easy-WRF WRF（Weather Research and Forecasting Model）模式是由NCEP，NCAR等科研机构中心着手开发的一种统一的中尺度天气预报模式。WRF模式系统具有的可移植，易维护，可扩充，高效率，方便等特点，使其成为改进从云尺度到各种不同...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"项目","slug":"项目","count":2,"path":"api/categories/项目.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"docker","slug":"docker","count":1,"path":"api/tags/docker.json"},{"name":"WRF模式","slug":"WRF模式","count":1,"path":"api/tags/WRF模式.json"},{"name":"安装","slug":"安装","count":1,"path":"api/tags/安装.json"},{"name":"easy-wrf","slug":"easy-wrf","count":1,"path":"api/tags/easy-wrf.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Easy-WRF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Easy-WRF</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Features</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Installation-amp-Usage\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Installation &amp; Usage</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%881%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-docker-pull-%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%88%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">方案1、使用 docker pull 拉取（推荐）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%882%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-docker-build\"><span class=\"toc-text\">方案2、使用 docker build</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-i